      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="0016_FL81799557"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb133">Wien XVIII. Spoettelgasse 7</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine>Dr. Stefan Zweig</addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb58">Wien VIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb249577">Kochgasse 8</rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="0017_FL81799694"/><date>2. 6. 0<unclear>9</unclear></date></dateline><salute>lieber Herr Doctor</salute></opener><p>wir nachtmahlen heute im <rs type="place" ref="#pmb74">Türkenschanzpark</rs>, etwa
                  <time>½ 9</time> – <time>9</time></p><p>Wollen Sie <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03803-1"/>hinko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03803-1"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1909-06-02" subtype="Cf"/>.</note>? Oder uns
               abholen? (Sind bis gegen <time>½ 9</time> zu Hause, von <time>8</time> an bereit.)
                  <rs type="person" ref="#pmb13055 #pmb13058">Wassermanns</rs> sind wahrscheinlich
               auch im <rs type="place" ref="#pmb74">T.p.</rs> Antwort <hi rend="underline" n="1">nicht nöthig</hi>.</p><closer>Herzlichst Ihr <signed>A. S.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
